<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="reference-n">reference <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'refrəns/    美 /'refrəns/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 提及；涉及：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Avoid <strong>making</strong> any <strong>reference to</strong> his illness. 
千万别提起他的病。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 查阅；参考：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Here is a memo for your reference when you answer the phones. 
这儿有一本备忘录供你接电话的时候参考。</p><footer>2010 福建</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>reference books</strong>
参考书</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>推荐信；推荐人</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-with-reference-to">in / with reference to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>关于；根据…而论：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In reference to your question about cost, the tickets for the film are 35 yuan each.
关于你询问的价格，那部电影的票价是每张35元。</p><footer>译林⑥ – 1</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>You’d better write down the phone number of that restaurant for future <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (refer).  （2012 江西改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. reference  </p></div>